# Delani

[Check it out](https://liliannjeri.github.io/Delani/)

## Description.

This is a web application that will allow customers to order different types of pizzas, with a crust they prefer as well as the toppings they would like on their pizza. This application also offers customers the option of having the pizza delivered to where they are

## Author.

> Lilian Njeri

## Screenshot

<img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LilianNjeri/Delani/master/assets/delani.png">

## Setup.

> `git clone https://github.com/LilianNjeri/Delani.git `

`extract the file`

`cd to the akan directory`

> `Open the index.html on your favorite browser`

## Technologies used.

- HTML5
- Javascript
- CSS
- JQuery

## BDD

The user can be able to make an order and select their preferred toppings,flavour,crust and size of their choice and a alert pops up. If they want a delivery they can be able to do so as well by giving their location details, name, phone number,thereafter there is delivery fee alert.

